                        <div class="heading-title heading-line-double text-center">
                            <h3>We have idenitified what we believe are Four Factors <br>that make <span>Workforce Optimization</span> so powerful:</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul>
                            <li class="size-20">Nothing matters unless it has a positive impact on company results. (Show Us The Money!)</li>
                            <li class="size-20">JOB TASKS are the leverage for Talent Develpment. (Job Tasks take front-row-center!)</li>
                            <li class="size-20">Accountability has two parts: process accountability and results accountability (Employee Reviews)</li>
                            <li class="size-20">Technology makes it easier  (that's why we offer P.E.R.F.O.R.M. at such a low cost!)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>Technology improvements have enabled HR professionals to leverage information in ways that just weren't possible before, and it is technology enablement that makes Workforce Optimization easier to achieve.</h4>
